Devel-WatchVars

This beta release introduces basic tracing of changes to individual
scalar variables, including those occuring in an array or hash.

Perl v5.10 is required.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Devel::WatchVars

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Devel-WatchVars

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Devel-WatchVars

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Devel-WatchVars

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Devel-WatchVars/


